<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;"><em>PM request. Placeholder. Be there soon!</em></span></p>
<p>Okay, so I'm not familiar with Competitive Eschatology in the slightest. In fact, I haven't even heard of it until now, so I went ahead and skimmed the page for some info and from what I gathered, it's a Canon where shit hits the fan, SCPs wreak havoc left and right and nothing goes according to plan. Unfortunately, since I'm not familiar with Competitive Eschatology, I can't comment on your article in how well it adheres to that hub, so this is just me judging your article by itself.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+Let's&nbsp;do&nbsp;it!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
